'''大港'''（Marina Grande）是[[卡普里岛|卡普里岛]]的主要港口，位于卡普里镇以北，[[索拉罗山|索拉罗山]]脚下。 

==历史==
位于卡普里岛的南岸的[[小港_(卡普里岛)|小港]]发展早于大港；[[奥古斯都|奥古斯都]]和[[提贝里乌斯|提贝里乌斯]]已经使用小港<ref name="DickensAinsworth1854">{{cite book|last1=Dickens|first1=Charles|last2=Ainsworth|first2=William Harrison|last3=Smith|first3=Albert|title=Bentley's miscellany|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=XuERAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA39|accessdate=5 July 2012|edition=Public domain|year=1854|publisher=Richard Bentley|pages=39–}}</ref>。罗马人在奥古斯都时期使用大港作为渔港，并在附近兴建海宫（Palazzo a Mare）<ref name="Valdés1996">{{cite book|last=Valdés|first=Giuliano|title=Naples, Capri, Sorrento: the pearls of the Gulf|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=GLCSefp0vYkC&pg=PA38|accessdate=4 July 2012|date=1 September 1996|publisher=Casa Editrice Bonechi|isbn=978-88-7009-713-9|page=38}}</ref>。提贝里乌斯强化了大港<ref name="ValdesFabbri2009">{{cite book|last1=Valdes|first1=Giuliano|last2=Fabbri|first2=Patrizia|title=Capri. Le Bellezze Di Capri. Ediz. Inglese|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ASRnvLfaHkkC&pg=PA17|accessdate=4 July 2012|year=2009|publisher=Casa Editrice Bonechi|isbn=978-88-476-2491-7|pages=17–18}}</ref>。卡普里岛也是希腊人登陆 [[坎帕尼亚|坎帕尼亚]]的第一个地点，卡普里的女人据说“有时仍然表现出明显的希腊特色”<ref name="(Firm)1903">{{cite book|last=Baedeker |first=Karl|title=Italy, Handbook for Travellers: Southern Italy ad Sicily, with excursions to the Lipari islands, Malta, Sardinia, Tunis, and Corfu. 14th rev. ed. 1903|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=mgdBAAAAYAAJ|accessdate=4 July 2012|year=1903|publisher=K. Baedeker|pages=156–8}}</ref> 在公元七世纪，公斯当休主教在大港附近去世，成为该岛的[[主保圣人|主保圣人]]<ref>Constantius of Capri is very poorly documented, but may be the same as Constantine I, Patriarch of Constantinople - see [http://www.santiebeati.it/dettaglio/91868 Santiebeati.it - San Costanzo di Capri] {{Wayback|url=http://www.santiebeati.it/dettaglio/91868 |date=20140829232119 }}.</ref>；[[圣公斯当休堂|圣公斯当休堂]]位于大港和阿纳卡普里之间。<ref name="RingSalkin1996">{{cite book|last1=Ring|first1=Trudy|last2=Salkin|first2=Robert M.|last3=Boda|first3=Sharon La|title=International Dictionary of Historic Places: Southern Europe|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=74JI2UlcU8AC&pg=PA121|accessdate=4 July 2012|date=1 January 1996|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-884964-02-2|pages=121–}}</ref>。

==地理==
大港位于卡普里岛的北岸。1928年之前，船只直接停在港湾，后来发展成为一个港口和海滨度假胜地，有岛上最大的沙滩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.italyguides.it/us/campania/isle_of_capri/port_marina_grande.htm|title=Port of Marina Grande|publisher=Italy Guides|accessdate=4 July 2012|archive-date=2012-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121125212837/http://www.italyguides.it/us/campania/isle_of_capri/port_marina_grande.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capri.com/en/s/marina-grande-2|title=Capri Marina Grande|publisher=Capri.com|accessdate=4 July 2012|archive-date=2014-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104094638/http://www.capri.com/en/s/marina-grande-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一个小广场俯瞰港口，环绕着卡普里特色的房子，包括露台，阳台，开放式游廊，和多种颜色的外墙，其中“庞贝红”是沿整个那不勒斯海岸最强烈的色彩<ref name="Valdés1996"/>。该镇的特色还有陡峭的斜坡和地中海植物。在西码头的尽头有一根 [[科林斯柱式|科林斯柱]]， 见证了罗马在该地区的存在<ref name="Valdés1996"/>。

==交通==
从大港有船前往大陆的[[那不勒斯|那不勒斯]]以及[[蓝洞_(卡布里岛)|蓝洞]]<ref name="FacarosPauls2004">{{cite book|last1=Facaros|first1=Dana|last2=Pauls|first2=Michael|title=Italy|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=XixojYgnRtsC&pg=PA893|accessdate=4 July 2012|date=1 May 2004|publisher=New Holland Publishers|isbn=978-1-86011-113-6|page=893}}</ref>。缆车由 SIPPIC经营<ref name="ShortCuts2012">{{cite book|author=Frommer's ShortCuts|title=Capri, Ischia and Procida, Italy: Frommer's ShortCuts|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=cZ-Sns8Xak8C&pg=PT17|accessdate=4 July 2012|date=5 April 2012|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-118-19895-7|pages=17–}}</ref>，连接港口与市中心的翁贝托一世广场<ref name="italyguides.it">{{cite web|url=http://www.italyguides.it/us/campania/isle_of_capri/funicolar.htm|title=Funicolar, isle of Capri|publisher=ItalyGuides.it - ComPart Multimedia|accessdate=5 July 2012|archive-date=2012-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121125204115/http://www.italyguides.it/us/campania/isle_of_capri/funicolar.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，还有巴士通往[[阿纳卡普里|阿纳卡普里]]<ref name="Capri. Ediz. Inglese">{{cite book|title=Capri. Ediz. Inglese|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=pYWWf1GOajUC&pg=PA7|accessdate=4 July 2012|year=2005|publisher=Casa Editrice Bonechi|isbn=978-88-476-1757-5|page=7}}</ref><ref name="BonettoQuintero2010">{{cite book|last1=Bonetto|first1=Cristian|last2=Quintero|first2=Josephine|title=Naples & the Amalfi Coast|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=I5_a1q8FobUC&pg=PA138|accessdate=4 July 2012|date=1 January 2010|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74104-509-3|page=138}}</ref>。截至2012年，到卡普里岛镇的单程火车票价格为1,5€<ref name="Frommer's2012">{{cite book|author=Frommer's|title=AARP Italy 2012|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=33jbBbLiCZcC&pg=PT624|accessdate=4 July 2012|date=24 May 2012|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-118-25836-1|page=624}}</ref>。

==旅游==
著名的酒店包括 Villa Marina Capri, Hotel Excelsior Parco Capri, Relais Maresca和布里斯托尔酒店。Ristorante Pizzeria Lo Zodiaco坐落在海滨。
每年九月中旬在大港庆祝 Madonna della Libera 节<ref name="Baedeker1903">{{cite book|last=Baedeker |first=Karl|title=Italy: Southern Italy and Sicily, with excursions to the Lipari islands, Malta, Sardinia, Tunis and Corfu. 13th rev. ed. 1900|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9ck9AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA157|accessdate=5 July 2012|edition=Public domain|year=1903|publisher=K. Baedeker|pages=157–}}</ref>。

